
'''''Sometimes in April''''' ni filime y'akozwe n'abany[[amerika]] muri 2005 ivuga kuri [[Itsembabwoko ry’u Rwanda ry’1994|jenoside]] yakorewe Abatutsi mu 1994 mu [[Rwanda]] <ref>https://www.facinghistory.org/books-borrowing/sometimes-april</ref><ref>https://africanfilmny.org/films/sometimes-in-april/</ref>, yanditswe kandi iyobowe n'umukinnyi wa filime wo [[Hayiti|muri Hayiti]] Raoul Peck. Abakinnyi bagize itsinda barimo Idris Elba, Oris Erhuero, Carole Karemera, na Debra Winger <ref>https://www.developmenteducationreview.com/issue/issue-5/sometimes-april</ref><ref>https://www.hulu.com/movie/sometimes-in-april-224c4c34-3c43-4047-92c6-2bf21dc33d10</ref>.

== Uko yateguwe ==
Bitandukanye na ''[[Hotel Rwanda]]'', yahawe igihembo cya PG-13 kandi ikaba yaravugaga mu buryo bwihishe inyuma ya jenoside aho kwerekana ku buryo bweruye<ref>https://www.films.com/ecTitleDetail.aspx?TitleID=213298</ref>, iyi filime yari izwiho kwerekana ihohoterwa rishingiye ku gitsina, ryayihaye TV-MA. Byongeye kandi, amashusho atandukanye yashyizwe mu Rwanda yafatiwe muri Kigali no hafi yayo, hagaragaramo ahantu nyaburanga nka Hotel des Mille Collines ndetse na kiliziya [[Kiriziya y'umuryango mutagatifu|ya Sainte-Famille]]<ref>https://www.worldcat.org/title/sometimes-in-april/oclc/58805300</ref> <ref>https://www.3continents.com/en/film/sometimes-in-april/</ref>.

Filime yabanje kwerekanwa kuri HBO . Nyuma yaje gutangazwa na PBS hanyuma isesengurwa  n’umunyamakuru jeff Greenfield hamwe na Paul Bonerwitz hamwe n’abandi<ref>https://www.tvguide.com/movies/sometimes-in-april/2000280433/</ref> <ref>https://www.filmaffinity.com/us/film711015.html</ref>.

